			<h3><span><a class="sharelink" rel="nofollow" href="#p452" onclick="return false;">Поделиться</a><strong>27</strong><a class="permalink" rel="nofollow" href="http://combcossack.0pk.ru/viewtopic.php?id=2#p452">2009-07-24 10:32:49</a></span></h3>
			<div class="container">
