			<h3><span><a class="sharelink" rel="nofollow" href="#p454" onclick="return false;">Поделиться</a><strong>29</strong><a class="permalink" rel="nofollow" href="http://combcossack.0pk.ru/viewtopic.php?id=2#p454">2009-07-24 10:35:54</a></span></h3>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="post-author">
