			<h3><span><a class="sharelink" rel="nofollow" href="#p678" onclick="return false;">Поделиться</a><strong>47</strong><a class="permalink" rel="nofollow" href="http://combcossack.0pk.ru/viewtopic.php?id=2#p678">2009-12-04 14:06:36</a></span></h3>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="post-author">
